@startuml
title Qualification: High-Level Experiment Execution

actor User
participant "Experiment Runner" as Runner
participant "Supervisor Agent (MCP)" as Supervisor
database "Knowledge Base" as KB
participant "LLM" as LLM
participant "Evaluation + Reporting" as Eval

User -> Runner: Provide issue/repository scenario
Runner -> Supervisor: Request supervised execution

Supervisor -> KB: Retrieve relevant guidance
KB --> Supervisor: Context summary

Supervisor -> LLM: Request planned solution
LLM --> Supervisor: Candidate change + rationale

Supervisor --> Runner: Supervised output

Runner -> Eval: Compute experiment metrics
Eval --> Runner: Results + artifacts

Runner --> User: Present high-level findings

@enduml